{
  "texts": [
    "The collaborative effectualness is improved, and human efforts are reduced while performing tasks with robots.",
    "Moreover, the robots gained a higher cognition rate in understanding human actions while analyzing the human motion intention levels.",
    "Different deep learning and machine learning models are employed to classify the motion intention using wearable devices, which are prone to different errors.",
    "Later, the time-variant classifiers are employed and used to analyze the sensor or mechanical signal.",
    "Due to the several limitations attained in the classical mechanism, it is essential to design an efficient mechanism to analyze the motion intentions of humans."
  ]
}